Resend Email Configuration
Note: Resend API key is now handled by Supabase Edge Functions
Add these to your Supabase project settings under Edge Functions secrets
RESEND_API_KEY=re_Z8Kr62XM_6TCL8Ftepm5X2urf6THFZ68U
FROM_EMAIL=noreply@strategyai.agency

Instructions:
1. Set up your Supabase project at https://supabase.com
2. Deploy the Edge Functions using: supabase functions deploy
3. Add your API keys to Supabase Edge Functions secrets:
   - OPENAI_API_KEY (from OpenAI)
   - RESEND_API_KEY (from Resend)
   - FROM_EMAIL (your verified sending domain)
4. Update VITE_SUPABASE_URL and VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY with your project details


